The multiple linear regression analysis function of the Design-Expert software was used to carry out regression analysis on the UCS of the CPB. In order to make the regression equation fit well and control and predict variables accurately, a multiple linear regression model of the following formula (1) is established:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
